⭐ 8. CTA-XVI (v1.1) — ONE SENTENCE VERSION

A self-adjusting geometry that keeps human meaning at the center,
model reasoning parallel,
and emotional proportion stabilized through a responsive membrane.

This is the “shape behind the shape” of SCN and SDS.

 
